verbose_text: A previous study showed that HNT is mainly influenced in endosperm development including endosperm cell number and size 11, and in present study, a COP9 signalosome complex subunit 3 (Q6ZJ47) showed a 4.6-fold upregulation in the HTL and was downregulated 1.5 (1/0.667)-fold in the HSL after HNT stress at early milky stage.
